      <title>自 1990 年以来首次跌破 160 日元后强劲反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/yen-slides-past-160-against-dollar-for-first-time-since-1990</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元在假期清淡的市场环境中波动，兑美元汇率突破 160 至 34 年来的最低水平，然后强劲反弹，引发当局可能进行干预的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/yen-slides-past-160-against-dollar-for-first-time-since-1990</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 02:14:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反向套利交易看到美元押注由新兴市场货币资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/carry-trade-gets-turned-on-its-head-stoking-rush-to-the-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几十年来，套利交易者以低利率借入美元，投资于收益较高的新兴市场货币。但现在这种趋势正在发生逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/carry-trade-gets-turned-on-its-head-stoking-rush-to-the-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
